---
<section id="about" class="section about-section" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-intro">
        <h2 id="about-heading" class="section-title">
          An open codebase and incubator for student developers
        </h2>
        <p class="about-desc">
          We are an independent developer collective building lightweight,
          privacy-first tools for the UPLB community, while mentoring the next
          generation of engineers and designers.
        </p>
        <p class="about-desc">
          We build tools that make campus enlistment, navigation, and
          administrative simulator processes smoother. Each of our tools is
          entirely open source, client-side, and designed to respect student
          privacy.
        </p>
        <p class="about-desc">
          uplb.tools also functions as a structured training sandbox. Student
          contributors collaborate via GitHub pull requests, learning software
          engineering fundamentals, design workflows, and release cycles.
        </p>
      </div>

      <ul class="about-principles">
        <li class="principle-item card">
          <h3>01 / Utility driven</h3>
          <p>
            We build to solve specific friction points in registration, schedule
            planning, and grading trackers.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li class="principle-item card">
          <h3>02 / Educational sandbox</h3>
          <p>
            We bridge the gap between academic theory and real-world development
            cycles using peer code reviews.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li class="principle-item card">
          <h3>03 / Zero tracking</h3>
          <p>
            No analytics engines, zero student tracking scripts, and no
            server-side databases.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-desc {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-body);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-principles {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .principle-item {
    padding: 1.25rem 1.35rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--brand-maroon);
  }

  .principle-item h3 {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .principle-item p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-body);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
